Class ClassificationDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.ClassificationDefinition
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClassBreaksDefinition, UniqueValueDefinition

    public class ClassificationDefinition
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    Class added v2.6 The super class for the classification definition objects used by the GenerateRendererTask class to generate data classes. This class has no constructor. Use ClassBreaksDefinition or UniqueValueDefinition instead.
    Author:
    Justin Merz
